kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n地盤先多<br />\n<br />\n幾乎個個月都有文章話 地盤好好搵<br />\n 一入行就1500蚊一日<br />\n勤力D開OT, 一個月12萬不是夢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前有個好似係一個月返足晒<br />\n係地盤訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e62891a56f0f2d2fed8f328aef5831f5e079a53","tid":128054,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"個個船長邊個船員<br />\n又氹人入行"},{"pid":"81ddca30fefe7e41566975113d49f8cf9a59fd86","tid":128054,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"搵十萬嘅機會應該難過地盤佬"},{"pid":"e9bc9b8767ed088191c0539e9d0a782ad7977a5c","tid":128054,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a61a56d9a6eede6946c2309064fec1b49eb21702","tid":128054,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行船係咪24小時船上過？</blockquote><br />\n唔係架，你鐘意可以跳落海喂下魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b82a9b093789a506f21895df1dfda8b46601c1","tid":128054,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菊花升得仲快</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0739f0c3c1d50e13652d709a249106d4c923ec","tid":128054,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"女友走佬<br />\n老婆勾佬<br />\n邊個肯做<br />\n單身就可以諗下"},{"pid":"8b4c84764b1ca9a1f7b777a1159d7ca6008c69cb","tid":128054,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbe04cd79d0ab5674b17a6fdce8fb630445a58d3","tid":128054,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"計返時薪 好撚低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682cbc758a474225be248b74bed79c27db6706be","tid":128054,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺唔覺呢幾年多左好多呢類善稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n地盤先多<br />\n<br />\n幾乎個個月都有文章話 地盤好好搵<br />\n 一入行就1500蚊一日<br />\n勤力D開OT, 一個月12萬不是夢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n現實扎鐵得1000 <br />\n<br />\n其他你話幾多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m555Di1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm555Di1.jpg&h=8f8e701a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n保安都萬五啦<br />\n<br />\n又閑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n扎鐵至少有2000-2500蚊一日<br />\n<br />\n不過係講緊師傅"},{"pid":"afdc5703214f6f3516e8a93f4db867bf8f2796e2","tid":128054,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"認真 無人無物既話真係可以考慮入行"},{"pid":"0b1ecb0b4f11f2c0db0e1695fee39c4013f37266","tid":128054,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計返時薪 好撚低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda664df38ad42b468aec26ab2f8e36e864bb688","tid":128054,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"昨日，「魯榮漁2682」號案在山東威海宣判，包括劉貴奪在內的5名被告人被判處死刑，1名被告人被判死緩，其餘被告人被判有期徒刑4年至15年。 2010年12月，該遠洋漁船載33名船員出海，2011年8月12日，被中國漁政船拖帶回港時，船上隻剩11名船員，歷時近兩年的偵辦和審理，11人被判殺害22名同伴。<br />\n<br />\n強度大收入低心懷不滿<br />\n<br />\n法院判決稱，2011年5、6月份，以船長李承權為首的33名船員，隨鑫發公司所屬的魯榮漁2682號漁船在東南太平洋秘魯、智利海域魷釣期間，被告人劉貴奪及包德格吉日胡（以下簡稱「包德」）等船員，認為魷釣時間長、強度大、收入低，心懷不滿，分別串聯被告人姜曉龍、劉成建、黃金波、王鵬及雙喜、戴福順、丁玉民等人，預謀劫持該船回國向公司討說法。<br />\n<br />\n劫船過程中，伙食長夏琦勇是第一個遇難者，被劉貴奪等人殺害並拋入海中。同年7月，行駛至夏威夷以西海域時，船員溫密、溫斗兩兄弟及其他3名船員被殺害拋入海中，另一船員被迫跳海，一人失蹤。次日，另有3名船員遇難。<br />\n<br />\n刀棍加害逼迫船員跳海<br />\n<br />\n2011年7月，劫船者內訌，劉貴奪打算除掉包德等人，船長李承權、崔勇、段志芳為自保，主動要求入夥。當晚，劉貴奪先指使人持刀捅刺包德，逼其跳海。繼而，雙喜、戴福順、包寶成、單國喜、邱榮華或被刺傷，或被迫跳海。<br />\n<br />\n7 月25日4時許，船艙進水、失去動力，王延龍失蹤。付義忠、官學軍、丁玉民、宋國春4人跳上木筏準備逃走，但隨洋流漂回漁船附近，4人被劉貴奪、李承權等人加害被迫跳海。次日有漁船接到其求救信號，向國家有關部門匯報後，7月29日，中國漁政118船拖帶「魯榮漁2682」號返航，隨後11人被抓獲。"},{"pid":"b538166462b6422775170784a44a447107278ad8","tid":128054,"uid":6041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咪公海</span></span>"},{"pid":"da4c11f66429b570a469e4d4b86dfc7e9403ae9e","tid":128054,"uid":39601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"上年Hanjin 先破產<br />\n其他船公司一係買更大既船， 一係船多到無人租，要去拆。。。<br />\n有冇咁多位比你升"},{"pid":"c511c6ab5744640f66b19222935dd67dd3e123a4","tid":128054,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"乜都無讀入行做船員有幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做開地盤都幾大隻"},{"pid":"ddedb8a577581cb052e1e588b7c388bde0b109cf","tid":128054,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺唔覺呢幾年多左好多呢類善稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n地盤先多<br />\n<br />\n幾乎個個月都有文章話 地盤好好搵<br />\n 一入行就1500蚊一日<br />\n勤力D開OT, 一個月12萬不是夢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n現實扎鐵得1000 <br />\n<br />\n其他你話幾多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m555Di1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm555Di1.jpg&h=8f8e701a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n保安都萬五啦<br />\n<br />\n又閑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n扎鐵至少有2000-2500蚊一日<br />\n<br />\n不過係講緊師傅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師傅起碼最快都要一年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\